{"tid":2100123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"即刻帶大家睇下SaveHK啲藍絲咩境環","createTime":"2020-07-08T23:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T06:05:16.000Z","uid":203873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"22871098d69f13a5578f53304172743d482fc1da","tid":2100123,"uid":203873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T23:02:01.000Z","msg":"話說的士佬就影咗條紋身佬冒驚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8c1WXsc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8c1WXsc.png&h=e0157cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後啲藍絲即刻衝曬上水爭住認叻懶醒<br />\n「黃絲唔用腦 如果係我我一定知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「藍絲最有獨立思考！我地唔睇新聞唔睇Twitter 唔睇驚驚打人！我地淨係睇叻哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fUEtOze.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfUEtOze.png&h=3c95a613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「依家驚曱做衰野點會同你講 你都憨鳩鳩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jjoqQND.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjjoqQND.png&h=ca5ed2b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「藍絲認證：全世界都係黃絲 咁撚憎就唔好冒驚啦」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dd9Q1Uk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdd9Q1Uk.png&h=71dd539f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實是但搵條友話自己係驚驚<br />\n你地即刻衝去幫佢含撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扮乜撚野馬後炮啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0f03455b5acfefe5e6c46cd8c1b8729cdeab1b","tid":2100123,"uid":96409,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T23:08:04.000Z","msg":"樓豬好靚仔"},{"pid":"eefb8bcfa62f7ad3d7446af45027c943495d6d20","tid":2100123,"uid":152944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T23:12:00.000Z","msg":"人唔笑警察都吠<img src=\"/assets/f